This is a really great feature.  I'm using your script for the hypertext cross-references in the [http://php-mode.sourceforge.net/php-mode.html HTML version of the PHP mode manual].  I can always be confident that it will redirect to the right place.  Look at the ##.html## rule in the [http://php-mode.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/php-mode/trunk/php-mode-src/Makefile Makefile] for PHP mode. -- AaronHawley


